*{{tl|ISSN link}} – Similar to this template, but without the "ISSN" text before the numbers. Also allows multiple ISSNs.
*The [[Help:Citation Style 1#Templates|Citation Style 1 and 2]] family of templates, which provide {{para|issn}} and {{para|eissn}} parameters
